<h2 id="tasks">Tasks</h2>

<p>Lists all the tasks assigned to the employee</p>

<h3 id="task-object">Task Object</h3>
<pre class="highlight http"><code><span class="nf">GET</span> <span class="nn">api/hrm/people/{id}/tasks</span> <span class="k">HTTP</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="m">1.1</span>
<span class="na">Accept</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">application/json</span>
<span class="na">Authorization</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">Token "YOUR ACCESS TOKEN"</span>

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json
</code></pre>
