<aside>POST api/hrm/people/{id}/tasks</aside>

<h4 id="returns">Returns</h4>

<p>If the call succeeds, it will return the task object. If any of the fields have invalid values, it will throw an error.</p>

<h3 id="delete-task">Delete Task</h3>
<pre class="highlight plaintext"><code>Sample Request
</code></pre>
<pre class="highlight http"><code><span class="nf">DELETE</span> <span class="nn">api/hrm/people/{profile_id}/tasks/{task_id}</span> <span class="k">HTTP</span><span class="o">/</span><span class="m">1.1</span>
<span class="na">Accept</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">application/json</span>
<span class="na">Authorization</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s">Token "YOUR ACCESS TOKEN"</span>

HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json
</code></pre>

<aside>DELETE api/hrm/people/{profile_id}/tasks/{task_id}</aside>
